TopicTitle: My New YouTube Channel with Kerbals

Articles.Content:
I have finally got a youtube channel been wanting to do this for so long. I am not that good and my editing is so so lol but I did it. My channel is all about video game commentary's. I feel guilty but I wanted some feedback on how I am doing so anything you can say would be really cool. Here is the channel and thanks for taking your time to help a lowly youtubin like myself. Of course the very first video I made was of Kerbal Space Program its not as hood as some of my other videos but I still had a lot of fun making it.
